parcel.description:
Web3vm is the Web3 vending machine and one-stop-shop for Web3 applications. This parcel is a waypoint for interacting with Web technologies like peer-to-peer (P2P) content storage and smart contracts on the public Ethereum blockchain. 

This parcel is designated for interacting with ERC20 and ERC721 token standards to distribute value and asset ownership within the Web3 ecosystem.
 
It is part of the WorldLaw, CityWide, and Swag0x projects presented by Web3vm and Web3 Legal Engineering.
